# Numbered source photos dropped in the project root as working files
# (01.고기.png, 02.그릴링.jpg, ...). They are the high-res originals; the
# web-sized derivatives that the site actually loads live in assets/img/.
# Keeping the originals out of git keeps the repo small — Vercel and Pages
# only ever need assets/img/.
/[0-9][0-9].*.png
/[0-9][0-9].*.jpg

# Local verification artifacts
/.playwright-mcp/
/*.png
!assets/**/*.png
